    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>FHIR</h2>
        <p>
            <a href="http://www.hl7.org/implement/standards/fhir/">FHIR</a> is the newest <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_Level_7">HL7</a> implementation.
            FHIR aims to be <a href="http://www.hl7.org/implement/standards/fhir/overview.html">simplify the implementation</a> of HL7v3 without sacrificing information integrity.            
        </p>
    </div>    
